size = Vector2i(641, 340)
dialog_text = "Plugin Reloader

A helper tool to quickly reload Godot editor plugins without restarting the editor.

- Reload individual plugins
- Reload all plugins
- Customizable keyboard shortcut for \"Reload All\".

Author: Rusith Welisara
License: MIT
Version: 1.1"

